WEBVTT

24:15.350 --> 24:17.540 line:80%
How could he possibly
marry a butcher girl,

24:17.540 --> 24:20.200 line:80%
giving her foot massages
and setting her bones?

24:20.370 --> 24:21.730 line:80%
I overthought it.

24:21.980 --> 24:24.230 line:80%
You haven't slept in days because of this.

24:24.230 --> 24:26.440 line:80%
Have a good sleep
on the way back to Jizhou.
